Group Travel & Events
Bring your Group to CoCo Key Resort!
We’re the perfect location for Orlando group travel and can easily accommodate your group’s needs. Complimentary motor coach parking and check in at our private Group Tour Lounge. Attractive group rates for 10 or more rooms, with special attention given to room assignments. Interior and exterior rooms are available.
Virtual Site Tour
:
https://youtu.be/e0s3ZsFX3dg
Book your next group by calling our Sales Department today:
Minerva Aponte, Director of Sales & Marketing
Direct: 321-206-4391
[email protected]
Group Travel Benefits: (10+ Rooms per Night)
-Each Guestroom includes 4 tickets to the Water Park
-Up to 5 ppl per room occupancy in the Tower (Interior Corridor Rooms)
-Motor coach Parking Available
-Dedicated group check in area
-Separate tour leader/ bus driver’s lounge
-Private 4,400 square foot multipurpose ballroom
-6 meeting rooms totaling 7,300 square feet
-Starbucks On Site with Grab and Go Items
-Catering Menus Available
Sports Groups
Bring your team to CoCo Key while attending your next sporting event! CoCo Key is a great place for those traveling with a team for a sporting event, or families traveling to compete in the Orlando area. We offer complimentary practice space, breakfast package options, and interior corridor rooms.
Youth Groups
Do something fun and different for your next youth outing!
The ideal setting for troops, schools, church groups, summer camps, and sports teams, we offer safe and fun activities in Orlando FL. Our single entry and exit water park with certified lifeguards allows parents to relax. We offer breakfast package options and interior corridor rooms.
When the sun sets, the fun heads indoors to our 6,500 square foot arcade. Looking for food options? Pre-purchase our Callaloo Grill meal vouchers. Each voucher includes an entrée, beverage, and dessert.
